The paper discusses a method for 3D map reconstruction using endoscopic capsule robots, which involves robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), graphics (cs.GR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of optical motion tracking and optical scanning, which further supports the likelihood of cs.CV and cs.GR.
